--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


-------------------
version 0.0.1(beta)
-------------------
* initial release
--------
Features
--------
* Allow to change Application and System folders name and folder locations 
  whatever the user want(IF CHANGES MADE - must config the index.php as 
  respective changes)
* Supports to implement multiple applications
* SET own Application MODE (Development/deployment) - to hide client side errors
* User can use your custom Error Handler and Exception handler or use the Error,
  Exception handler already given
* System Timer Control(Enable/Disable)
* Autoload any libraries or helpers or models
* Multiple URL routing
* Route URI dashes ( it convert -(dash or minus) symbol to _(under_score) )
* Multi-languages implementation - world wide multiple communication languages
* Database query in Plain SQL, Active records method, method-chaining
* Multiple Database groups and Connections
* 3 Database Drivers Included : MYSQLI-Procedural, MYSQLI-Object Oriented, PDO
* html offline user guide added
--------------------------------
Following HELPERS are Included
--------------------------------
* Auto Copy Right (copyright year updated automatically every year)
* IP Address (Automatically finds client IP Address)
